    ],
    "content": "When the user says \"which knives cost more than X\" or \"knives over X\" or \"show me knives priced above X\", this is a LIST with a purchase_price filter, NOT an aggregate. Use intent=list, metric=count, with a filter on purchase_price > X. The sort should be purchase_price desc.",
